svg.text: When a string of brutal murders terrorizes London, it doesn't take long for legendary detective Sherlock Holmes and his crime-solving partner, Dr. Watson, to find the killer, Lord Blackwood.A devotee of the dark arts, Blackwood has a bigger scheme in mind, and his execution plays right into his plans. ยง
